    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the vegetables are cooking, add the <strong>basmati rice </strong>to a pot of plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the rice for 7-8 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the rice and return it to the pan with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> (or <strong>butter alternative</strong>)</p>",
